Get Differential Expression

Source: R/convenience.R
getDatasetDE.Rd

Retrieves the differential expression resultSet(s) associated with the dataset. If there is more than one resultSet, it will show the options and prompt the user to choose one.

getDatasetDE(dataset)

Arguments

dataset

A dataset identifier.

Value

A data table with differential expression values

Examples

getDatasetDE("GSE2018")
